HEADWORD: Nectareous
<hw>Nec*ta"re"ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of, pertaining
to, containing, or resembling nectar; delicious; nectarean.</def>
<rj><au>Pope.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

